docs: Update installation notes to mention `pyicu`

In issue #10, it was reported that `polyglot` will fail to load if
`pyicu` is not installed.  The installation documentation incorrectly
names `libicu-dev` as the dependency required to satisfy this
requirement.

Whilst we're here, give the equivalent commands for Python3 users on
Debian/Ubuntu.
